    "Levine et al.",
    "21 evaluated the diagnostic and triage accuracies of GPT-3 for 48 validated case vignettes of both common consumer health and medical research.",
    "We proposed a human evaluation rubric enabling physicians and laypeople to perform detailed assessment of model answers.",
    "Our initial model, Flan-PaLM, achieved strong performance across multiple-choice benchmarks.",
    "However, human evaluation revealed further work was necessary to ensure factual long-form answers aligned with human values and expectations in this safety-critical domain (a process generally referred to as 'alignment')."
